<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287595>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Habitus of Larinioides species. Letters indicate columns; numbers indicate rows. 1 — L. jalimovi; 2 — L. ixobolus; 3 — L. sericatus; 4 — L. patagiatus. A, B—females; C, D—males; A, C—dorsal side; B, D—ventral side." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287595/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287597>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Prolateral view of the second pair of male legs of Larinioides species. A— L. jalimovi; B— L ixobolus; C— L. sericatus; D— L. patagiatus; E— L. chabarovi, F— L. cornutus; G— L. folium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287597/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287606>
    dc:description "FIGURES 26 – 32. Epigyne of Larinioides species. Letters—columns. Numbers—rows. 26 — L. jalimovi; 27 — L. ixobolus; 28 — L. sericatus; 29 — L. patagiatus; 30 — L. cornutus; 31 — L. folium; 32 — L. chabarovi. A – D—posterior, E—lateral, F—dorsal view. A, C—before maceration; B, D – F—after maceration in NaOH solution. BL = basal lamella, LL = lateral lamella, SC = scapus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287606/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287599>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Median apophysis of male palp of Larinioides species. A— L. jalimovi; B— L. ixobolus; C— L. sericatus, arrow pointed to the spur from different view; D— L. patagiatus; E— L. chabarovi; F— L. cornutus; G— L. folium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287599/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287604>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21 – 24. Male embolic division of Larinioides sericatus and L. patagiatus. Letters indicate columns; numbers indicate rows. 21, 22 — L. sericatus; 23, 24 — L. patagiatus; 21, 23 — before maceration; 22, 24 — after maceration in NaOH solution; A, B—prolateral view; C, D—retrolateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287604/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287598>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Conductor of male palp of Larinioides species. A— L. jalimovi; B— L. ixobolus; C— L. sericatus; D— L. patagiatus; E— L. chabarovi; F— L. cornutus; G— L. folium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287598/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

